---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Simpler Recipes"
  description="Privacy policy for Simpler Recipes website and browser extension."
>
  <main id="main-content" class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
      <nav class="mb-8">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-sand-600 hover:text-sand-900 transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="ml-1">Back</span>
        </a>
      </nav>

      <article class="bg-sand-50 rounded-2xl shadow-md p-6 md:p-10">
        <header class="mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-sand-200">
          <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight-headline text-sand-900 mb-2">
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="text-sand-500 text-sm">Last updated: January 17, 2025</p>
        </header>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">Introduction</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>
                <strong>Simpler Recipes</strong> is committed to respecting your privacy. This policy explains
                how we handle information when you use our website at simpler.recipes and our browser extension.
              </p>
              <p>
                The short version: <strong>We collect minimal data and don't sell or share your personal information.</strong>
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">What we collect</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <h3 class="text-sand-800 font-medium text-sm mt-4 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Website (simpler.recipes)</h3>
              <p>When you use our website, we collect:</p>
              <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span><strong>Recipe URLs you submit</strong> — These are processed on our servers to extract recipe
                  data. We do not store the URLs or extracted recipes beyond the immediate request.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span><strong>Anonymous analytics</strong> — We use Google Analytics to understand how people use the
                  site (page views, general location, device type). This data is aggregated and cannot identify you personally.</span>
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h3 class="text-sand-800 font-medium text-sm mt-4 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Browser Extension</h3>
              <p>
                The Simpler Recipes browser extension processes recipes <strong>entirely on your device</strong>.
                No data is sent to our servers or any third party. We do not collect, store, or transmit:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>The pages you visit</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>The recipes you extract</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>Any personal information</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                The extension only activates when you click its icon and only reads recipe data (Schema.org markup)
                from the current page.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">What we don't collect</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>We do not collect or have access to:</p>
              <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>Your name, email, or contact information (we don't have accounts)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>Payment information (our service is free)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>Browsing history</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>Cookies for tracking or advertising</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">How we use data</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>The limited data we collect is used only to:</p>
              <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>Process your recipe extraction requests (website only)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>Understand aggregate usage patterns to improve the service</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>Maintain and secure the service</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                We do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties for marketing or advertising purposes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>Our website uses:</p>
              <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>
                    <strong>Google Analytics</strong> — For anonymous usage statistics. You can opt out using a
                    browser extension like{' '}
                    <a
                      href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout"
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noopener noreferrer"
                      class="text-sand-700 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sand-900"
                    >
                      Google Analytics Opt-out
                    </a>.
                  </span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-sand-400 flex-shrink-0">–</span>
                  <span>
                    <strong>Vercel</strong> — For hosting. See{' '}
                    <a
                      href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy"
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noopener noreferrer"
                      class="text-sand-700 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sand-900"
                    >
                      Vercel's Privacy Policy
                    </a>.
                  </span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p>The browser extension does not use any third-party services.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">Data retention</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>
                Recipe URLs submitted to our website are processed in real-time and not stored. Shared recipe
                links expire after 7 days. Analytics data is retained according to Google Analytics' standard
                retention policies.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">Your rights</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>
                Since we collect minimal data and don't maintain user accounts, there is little personal data
                to access or delete. If you have questions about your data, contact us and we'll help however we can.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>
                We may update this policy from time to time. We'll note the date of the latest revision at the
                top of this page.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-sand-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
            <div class="text-sand-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
              <p>
                Questions about this privacy policy? Reach out at{' '}
                <a
                  href="mailto:privacy@simpler.recipes"
                  class="text-sand-700 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sand-900"
                >
                  privacy@simpler.recipes
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
